	<h2>Teed: Portraits of [South] Sudan</h2>
	<p>
		<em class="project--brief">Independent study at <a href="http://www.artcenter.edu">Art Center College of Design</a> under Professor Gloria Kondrup</em>
		<span>In my final semester, <a href="http://www.designmattersatartcenter.org">Designmatters</a>, the design for social change initiative at Art Center sponsored a show of photographs I took in South Sudan. Many of the images were taken just a few months before South Sudan became an nation in January 2011 and capture a people awaiting their independence.</span>
